Package com.github.games647.craftapi.resolver.http

Class RotatingSourceFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.net.SocketFactory
      • javax.net.ssl.SSLSocketFactory
        • com.github.games647.craftapi.resolver.http.RotatingSourceFactory
  • public class RotatingSourceFactory
extends SSLSocketFactory
    Implementation for rotating outgoing IPv4 addresses. It binds the next available IPv4 address to the socket generated by the given oldFactory.
